---
import Layout from "../../../layouts/Layout.astro";

const lang = "en";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Flux Blog" lang={lang}>
    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto py-12 prose prose-stone dark:prose-invert">
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p>Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US')}</p>
        <p>Your privacy is important to us. It is Flux Blog's policy to respect your privacy regarding any information we may collect from you across our website.</p>
        <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We only ask for personal information when we truly need it to provide a service to you. We collect it by fair and lawful means, with your knowledge and consent.</p>
        <h2>Data Retention</h2>
        <p>We only retain collected information for as long as necessary to provide you with your requested service. What data we store, we’ll protect within commercially acceptable means to prevent loss and theft.</p>
    </section>
</Layout>
